### 1. Structure
- Use appropriate HTML5 elements
- Maintain proper heading hierarchy
- Implement ARIA labels when needed
- Ensure proper document outline

### 2. Examples
```astro
<section aria-labelledby="section-title">
  <h2 id="section-title">Section Title</h2>
  <!-- Content -->
</section>
```

## Interactive Elements

@rules [
    {
        "id": "button_semantics",
        "rule": "Use semantic <button> for actions",
        "severity": "error"
    },
    {
        "id": "link_semantics",
        "rule": "Use <a> for navigation",
        "severity": "error"
    },
    {
        "id": "focus_states",
        "rule": "Implement focus states",
        "severity": "warning"
    }
]

### 1. Buttons and Links
- Use semantic `<button>` for actions
- Use `<a>` for navigation
- Implement focus states
- Ensure sufficient contrast

### 2. Implementation
```astro
<button 
  class="btn-primary"
  aria-label="Submit form"
>
  Submit
</button>
```

## Images and Media

