### 1. Alt Text
- Provide descriptive alt text
- Use empty alt for decorative images
- Consider context in descriptions
- Maintain consistency

### 2. Examples
```astro
<img 
  src="logo.jpg" 
  alt="Dale Rogers Portfolio Logo"
  width="200"
  height="100"
/>
```

